g.text: The United States ranked #1 in the Global Entrepreneurship Index with score of 84%, beating out Switzerland and Canada.
Global Entrepreneurship IndexSource:The Global Entrepreneurship and Development Institute
The United States ranked #1 in the Global Entrepreneurship Index with score of 84%. Sample Data Only*
Switzerland maintains the #1 position in the Global Entrepreneurship Index at 81%.Sample Data Only*
Israel ranked #1 in the Global Entrepreneurship Index with score of 80%. Sample Data Only*

The 2017 Global Entrepreneurship Index (GEI) provides key information for policymakers and government leaders worldwide to strengthen their digital ecosystems and promote high-growth, high-impact entrepreneurship. The authors estimate that improving conditions to help entrepreneurs create new companies could add $22 trillion to the global economy.
